Dialogue: 0,00:08:39.280,00:08:44.760,辉英,,0,0,0,,representation is that xn is equal to a summation where all the a i's are zero
Dialogue: 0,00:08:44.760,00:08:51.300,辉英,,0,0,0,,except for a n which is 1. So xn is equal to xn. And also it has a different
